{"tid":425919,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"生銹路牌塌下　擊傷女經紀","createTime":"2017-10-06T07:09:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-06T07:51:46.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"cfbd98c79e0a76da4e2efea664e1d228808a82ad","tid":425919,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T07:09:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20174006&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20171006\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20174006%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20171006&d=RkDpb%2Fugp%2FKDARkKXTmhTlzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=18fc665d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20174006%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20171006&h=aabe7b08\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20174006&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20171006</a><br />\n<br />\n生銹路牌塌下　擊傷女經紀<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171006/large/a1002a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171006%2Flarge%2Fa1002a.gif&h=54a3c283&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被塌下路牌擊中的女保險經紀受傷倒地。讀者提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一名女保險經紀昨在上水清河邨商場對開的清曉路派傳單期間，身旁一支連着路牌的鐵柱突塌下，女事主閃避不及被擊中頭部，當場受傷倒地，救護車到場將她送院治理。現場所見，該支路牌在近地面位置斷裂，懷疑因日久失修生銹而倒塌。<br />\n<br />\n任職保險代理的姓鍾女傷者（40歲），事後在醫院向《蘋果》表示，經初步檢查敷治後仍感暈眩，左邊頭部「仲痛痛哋」。她憶述，昨午3時許偕3名同事到清河邨商場對開單車徑派傳單，「第一次喺嗰度派，大家一直行嚟行去派傳單」，至5時許，她突被單車徑旁的圓形路牌擊中頭部，「有幾秒係不省人事，過咗陣同事嗌我，我先知自己暈咗」。<br />\n<br />\n「利嗰邊劈落嚟死梗」<br />\n<br />\n鍾形容事件突如其來，回想事發一刻仍有餘悸，直言「冇諗過條柱會冧，完全冇先兆」，又指幸好路牌倒塌時，不是路牌邊擊中她頭部，否則事件不堪設想，「真係感恩&hellip;&hellip;好彩係板嗰邊壓落嚟，如果係利啲嗰邊劈落嚟，我應該死梗，分開兩邊」。<br />\n現場所見，塌下的路牌近地面位置斷裂，斷口有生銹霉爛現象，疑是日久失修所致，而附近多支路牌亦有類似生銹情況，警方事後封鎖線現場調查。街坊稱現場平日途人眾多，希望當局正視問題，從速檢驗場路牌情況，以策安全。<br />\n<br />\n■記者姜偉康"},{"pid":"4082016cf671be3d8c3dc8e423839d10df4ec3a7","tid":425919,"uid":35667,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T07:26:38.000Z","msg":"留底既係一份心意<br />\n唔係負擔"},{"pid":"87f386d0cc1392673ac12e8853969be463f8dc8e","tid":425919,"uid":101976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T07:26:54.000Z","msg":"死神來了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea2ee5fe592a2ece52fb37ae684d0e03abd9f74e","tid":425919,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T07:44:52.000Z","msg":"又會咁岩做保險，拎自己黎賣廣告啦"},{"pid":"a858c907e1d9d2eb9c2fc966e269031807c7bfcc","tid":425919,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T07:46:26.000Z","msg":"著裙的話有底褲睇"},{"pid":"9138499aa4b6707cede9f87c939e2b12619113b0","tid":425919,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T07:48:08.000Z","msg":"唔知佢自己有冇幫自己買保險呢"},{"pid":"33e39adcf35162ba86e4bb99293dba091dd041d8","tid":425919,"uid":75100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T07:49:52.000Z","msg":"死神來了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c8f55a8d42be718ec39bb10f28bb408988a8bf6","tid":425919,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T07:50:51.000Z","msg":"諗起尼泊爾地震個保險廣告"},{"pid":"ed818bad9f5546d24b123d5fd5692dce534496f0","tid":425919,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T07:51:05.000Z","msg":"皇天擊殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bed91f60618671f21f205abc895488f9b5bb940","tid":425919,"uid":69886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T07:51:46.000Z","msg":"保險狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}